Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:32.90,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Do you still have my drawings?{\r}\N你那儿还有我的画吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:35.17,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Yes.{\r}\N有的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:38.45,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Please give them to my boy...{\r}\N请把它们留给我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.48,0:01:43.26,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}to help him remember me.{\r}\N让他能记住我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:50.55,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Even when I'm gone...{\r}\N就算我去了天堂...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:54.17,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I'll be watching over you{\r}\N我也会时时保佑你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.82,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}my little masterpiece.{\r}\N我的心肝宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:01.44,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}God has so much planned for you.{\r}\N上帝已为你计划好了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:06.56,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I love you.{\r}\N我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:09.60,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I love you, Nello.{\r}\N我爱你 尼洛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:13.96,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I'll always be with you.{\r}\N我永远都和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:30.47,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Can you hear your mother?{\r}\N你听到你母亲说话了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:36.76,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}You must listen with your heart.{\r}\N你得用你的心去听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:43.08,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}She talks through your God-given talent.You even make me look good!{\r}\N神赐予你天赋使你能跟她讲话 你甚至都让我看上去年轻不少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.58,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Come on! I'll race you to the village.{\r}\N来吧! 我们看谁先跑回村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:48.83,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Come on!{\r}\N快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:52.90,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}- I'll beat you, Grandpa! - Look at him go.{\r}\N-我肯定跑得比你快 爷爷! -瞧你跑得多快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:55.49,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I'll beat you!{\r}\N我要得第一啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:13.21,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}- Here you are, Nello. - Thank you.{\r}\N-给你 尼洛 -谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.29,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Good day.{\r}\N日安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:28.84,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}- Good morning, madam. - Hello. And good day to you, sir.{\r}\N-早上好 女士 -你好 也祝你有愉快的一天 小先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.77,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}What have you been up to now?{\r}\N你最近做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:37.77,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Have you forgotten how old you are?{\r}\N你这把老骨头有多脆都给你玩忘记了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:39.08,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Oh, yeah.{\r}\N噢 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:43.23,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I prefer to think of my spirit as ageless.{\r}\N我更愿意认为我精神不老
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.87,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}- Here. - No, no. The boy, the boy.{\r}\N-给你钱 -不 不 给那孩子 他是掌柜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:50.80,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Thank you, sir.{\r}\N谢谢你 小先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.55,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}If you please.{\r}\N请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.24,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Thank you, ma'am.{\r}\N谢谢您 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.37,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Just a moment.{\r}\N稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.66,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}That's for you.{\r}\N这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.41,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}If you please.{\r}\N也请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:04.74,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}- Thank you, ma'am. - And this too.{\r}\N- 太谢谢您了 女士 - 来 这个也给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.38,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Move!{\r}\N给我跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:23.89,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Move!{\r}\N跑起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.25,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}You know what, Nello?{\r}\N你知道吗 尼洛?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:56.11,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I think tonight we'll have veal stew.Minus the veal, of course.{\r}\N我想我们今天晚上能吃炖菜了 当然还是一样没有牛肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.16,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Grandpa, look.{\r}\N爷爷 看呐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.14,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Is he alive?{\r}\N他还活着吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:12.81,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Barely.{\r}\N就剩一口气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:15.65,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Who could do such a thing?{\r}\N谁会干这么残忍的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:19.54,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Some men have no respect for life.{\r}\N糟蹋生命的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:23.51,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}This is a dog of Flanders.{\r}\N这是佛兰德斯犬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:27.38,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}A hardworking breed of dog.{\r}\N是一种勤奋工作的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:32.40,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}We can't just leave him here.Can we keep him?{\r}\N我们不能把他留在这儿 我们能养他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:34.17,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}He can share my food.{\r}\N他跟我吃一份儿就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:47.33,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}He's not hungry.{\r}\N他还不饿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.20,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Well, it takes energy to eat.{\r}\N这个 吃东西也是要费力气的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:51.58,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Leave it.{\r}\N放着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.42,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Maybe later.{\r}\N过一会儿他就吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:00.96,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}What else can we do?{\r}\N我们还能做些什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:04.50,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}A little broth and a lot of love.{\r}\N能给它点肉汤 还有爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:07.21,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}He's starved for both.{\r}\N这两项他都缺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:10.62,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I love you so much. So you'll have to get better, okay?{\r}\N我很爱你啊 所以你要快点好起来 好不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:23.00,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}It's a magic necklace. It'll heal you.{\r}\N这是条神奇的项链 它能治好你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:33.20,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}What's that?{\r}\N那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.23,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}You should draw what you hope to see.{\r}\N你应该画你想看到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:54.35,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}It's too sad, Nello.{\r}\N这表情太悲伤了 尼洛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.59,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}That's better.{\r}\N这还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.98,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Grandpa, he's drinking it! He's getting better.{\r}\N爷爷 他喝东西啦 他要好起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:35.04,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Well, I'm going to get me one of those magic necklaces!{\r}\N好吧 我也要去弄一条神奇的项链
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.64,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}That's the spirit.{\r}\N这样才对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.58,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}So, what do you think?{\r}\N看看 你觉得怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:57.45,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Never underestimate the power of love,my boy.{\r}\N永远别低估爱的力量 我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:04.13,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}He needs a name.{\r}\N得给他取个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:06.28,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Patrasche.{\r}\N帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.60,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Your mother's middle name.{\r}\N是你母亲中间的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.94,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Then they'll both be watching over me.{\r}\N这样他们俩就都能保佑我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:22.78,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Grandfather, maybe you should see a doctor.{\r}\N爷爷 也许你该去看看医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:27.43,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}For him to tell me something I already know, that I'm old and tired?{\r}\N听他说我又老又虚弱? 我已经知道了啊
