Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:47.44,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Why don't you take Patrasche and introduce him to Aloise?{\r}\N你为什么去不带帕奇去找阿洛伊斯玩呢?
