Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.77,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Is it because you have to help your grandfather?{\r}\N是因为你要给你爷爷帮忙吗?
