Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:05.52,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}She wanted you to have it so you would always remember her.{\r}\N她想让你保留着 这样你就能永远记住她了
