Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:14.06,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Seems like yesterday I was walking along the canal with your mother.{\r}\N想想和你妈妈一起在运河边散步 就好像是发生在昨天一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:18.63,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}This was your mother's favorite place.{\r}\N这曾是你妈妈最喜欢的地方
