Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.21,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}This was your grandmother, Rosa.{\r}\N这是你的奶奶罗莎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.59,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Influenza took her from me.{\r}\N流感从我身边夺走了她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:59.09,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}But, that is my favorite picture.{\r}\N但这个才是我最喜欢的一幅画
