Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.05,1:21:35.57,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Nicholas, what are you going to do?{\r}\N尼古拉斯 你打算怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.22,1:21:37.73,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I'm going to find Nello.{\r}\N我要去找到尼洛
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.75,1:21:41.53,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I've done that boy a terrible wrong, Anna.{\r}\N我完完全全的错怪了那个孩子 安娜
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.25,1:21:46.14,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Nello!{\r}\N尼洛!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.74,1:21:49.67,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Nello!{\r}\N尼洛!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.59,1:22:24.02,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}- Nello, where are you? - Answer me, boy!{\r}\N-尼洛 你在哪? -回答我 孩子!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.75,1:23:25.06,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Find him!{\r}\N一定要找到他!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.70,1:23:37.77,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Patrasche! What are you doing here?{\r}\N帕奇 你在这干什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.38,1:24:19.73,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}This has been the coldest Christmas ever.{\r}\N今年是最冷的一个圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.73,1:24:24.86,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}But it hasn't chilled the hearts of our parishioners. The Lord has been bountiful.{\r}\N但严寒并没有冰封教区居民的心 因为我们的主终是慷慨的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.55,1:24:50.10,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Are you ready, Patrasche?{\r}\N准备好了么 帕奇
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.45,1:25:13.52,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Oh, Patrasche, not enough light.{\r}\N哦 帕奇 不够亮
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.50,1:25:15.76,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I can't see it.{\r}\N我看不到
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.43,1:25:36.02,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}It's even colder in here than it is outside.{\r}\N这里比外边更冷
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.52,1:25:39.04,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Must be the stones.{\r}\N一定是因为是这些石头
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.13,1:25:47.38,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}It isn't long till the sun rises, Patrasche.{\r}\N天快要亮了 帕奇
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.83,1:25:51.86,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Once we see his masterpiece...{\r}\N只要我们能看到他的杰作...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.73,1:25:55.54,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}we can join Mother...{\r}\N我们就能去找妈妈...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.35,1:25:57.35,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}and Grandfather.{\r}\N还有爷爷
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.25,1:26:01.57,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}The only people who still love us.{\r}\N仅有的两个仍然爱我们的人
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.04,1:26:37.69,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Look.{\r}\N看
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.87,1:26:46.39,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}That's it. I'm sure Nello went to see the Rubens.{\r}\N看那边 我确信尼洛会去看鲁本斯
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.17,1:27:18.28,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Patrasche.{\r}\N帕奇
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.98,1:27:19.60,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Look.{\r}\N看
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.26,1:27:32.71,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Master Rubens?{\r}\N鲁本斯大师
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.89,1:27:37.05,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}So, what do you think?{\r}\N你觉得怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.28,1:27:41.13,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}It's...{\r}\N它
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.33,1:27:43.49,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}It's magnificent.{\r}\N非常宏伟
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.92,1:27:46.38,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I quite liked your circus painting too.{\r}\N我也很喜欢你那副关于描绘马戏团的油画
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.65,1:27:47.93,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}You saw my painting?{\r}\N你看到我的画了?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.41,1:27:52.85,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I've taken a strong interest in your artistic career, Nello.{\r}\N我对你的艺术非常感兴趣 尼洛
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.68,1:27:54.16,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}But...{\r}\N但是...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.17,1:27:56.95,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}why didn't I win the art contest?{\r}\N为什么我赢不了美术比赛
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.76,1:28:00.34,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}You didn't want to just win, did you?{\r}\N你并不是只想要赢得比赛 对么?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.70,1:28:04.79,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}No. And I can't blame you.{\r}\N不 我不会怪你的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.53,1:28:09.78,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}You want to be accepted, Nello.{\r}\N你希望被认可 尼洛
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.72,1:28:12.37,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}To feel loved.{\r}\N希望感受到被爱的滋味
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.81,1:28:15.76,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}What you want, all men seek.{\r}\N你所追求的 所有人都在追寻
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.22,1:28:21.14,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}In 200 years from now, when people will admire our paintings...{\r}\N两百年之后 当人们在赞美我们的作品时...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.41,1:28:25.14,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}you really think anyone will remember that silly contest?{\r}\N你真的认为还会有人记得那个愚蠢的比赛么?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.02,1:28:27.91,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Will I be a great artist?{\r}\N我会成为一个伟大的艺术家么?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.22,1:28:31.80,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}People will be inspired by you for years to come.{\r}\N人们总有一天会受到你的启迪
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.64,1:28:38.24,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I know how you feel.{\r}\N我明白你的感受
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.83,1:28:40.43,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I left home once...{\r}\N我曾经离开家...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.06,1:28:43.44,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}went to Italy for eight years.{\r}\N去意大利待了8年
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.01,1:28:45.65,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Then my mother got sick.{\r}\N之后我的母亲生病
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.70,1:28:49.93,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}By the time I came back here, she was dead.{\r}\N等到我回到这里时 她已经过世
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.45,1:28:51.95,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}My mother's dead too.{\r}\N我的母亲也去世了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.14,1:28:54.48,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}You were her hero.{\r}\N你是她的偶像
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.68,1:28:59.36,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Mary Daas. She's a very fine artist.{\r}\N玛丽·达斯 她是一个很棒的艺术家
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.70,1:29:02.38,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}- You knew my mother? - Of course.{\r}\N-你知道我的母亲? -当然
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.64,1:29:05.92,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Why do you think I've taken such a strong interest in you?{\r}\N不然你认为我为什么会对你这么感兴趣?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.04,1:29:10.18,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}- Master? - Yes?{\r}\N-大师? -什么事?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.58,1:29:14.98,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}If it's all right, Patrasche and I would like to come with you.{\r}\N如果可以 我和帕奇想跟您一起走
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.30,1:29:18.62,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}No one cares.{\r}\N没人关心我
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.48,1:29:21.67,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Do you really think you're not loved?{\r}\N你真的认为没有人爱你么?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.55,1:29:27.85,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Then you've yet to learn to see like a true artist:{\r}\N那你要学会像一个真正的艺术家一样去观察:
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.56,1:29:30.10,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}With your heart.{\r}\N用你的心去观察
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.27,1:30:07.71,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}My son.{\r}\N我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.62,1:30:16.09,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}My son.{\r}\N我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.09,1:30:18.79,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}My beautiful son.{\r}\N我漂亮的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.86,1:30:30.80,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}"The Lord is my shepherd.{\r}\N耶和华是我的牧者
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.14,1:30:32.88,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I shall not be in want.{\r}\N我必不至于匮乏
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.44,1:30:35.79,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}He makes me lie down in green pastures.{\r}\N他使我躺卧在青草地上
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.26,1:30:38.83,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}He leads me beside quiet waters.{\r}\N领我在可安歇的水域
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.54,1:30:41.17,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}He restores my soul.{\r}\N他使我的灵魂苏醒
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.65,1:30:47.32,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}He guides me in the paths of righteousness for His name's sake.{\r}\N他以他的名义指引我走向正义之路
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.55,1:30:52.93,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Even though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death... "{\r}\N即使我走过被死亡阴影笼罩的山谷
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.18,1:31:20.81,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I went to find the boy...{\r}\N我去找了这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.12,1:31:24.22,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}who truly deserved to win the contest...{\r}\N比赛真正的获胜者...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.22,1:31:26.27,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}but I was too late.{\r}\N但太晚了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.51,1:31:30.92,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}We were all too late, sir.{\r}\N我们都来晚了 先生
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.86,1:31:32.85,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Are you his mother?{\r}\N您是他的母亲么?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.52,1:31:35.01,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}His mother lies there.{\r}\N他的母亲长眠于此
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.47,1:31:38.40,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}And his grandfather lies there.{\r}\N还有他的祖父 在那边
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.75,1:31:41.55,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}The boy had no other family.{\r}\N这个孩子没有其他的家人
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.69,1:31:43.73,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Where is his father?{\r}\N他的父亲呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.51,1:31:48.96,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Most people believe that Nello's father lived in another city...{\r}\N大多数人认为尼洛的父亲住在另一个城市...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.94,1:31:52.47,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}and that he died after Nello was born.{\r}\N他在尼洛出生后就死了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.93,1:31:54.28,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}And what do you believe, madam?{\r}\N您相信么 夫人?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.55,1:31:57.01,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I believe what his mother confided in me.{\r}\N我相信他的母亲告诉我的话
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.96,1:32:00.59,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}That she had been in love...{\r}\N她爱上了...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.62,1:32:04.96,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}with a prominent artist from this city.{\r}\N来自这个城市的一个知名艺术家
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.04,1:32:12.50,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I want to live my life.{\r}\N我想过自己的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.84,1:32:18.61,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}But I don't want to leave you,Grandfather, or you, Mama.{\r}\N但我不想离开你们 外祖父 还有妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.06,1:32:20.50,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Sweetheart.{\r}\N甜心
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.28,1:32:24.14,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}You are loved, my son.{\r}\N有人在爱着你 我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.02,1:32:27.27,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I'll always be here waiting for you.{\r}\N我会一直在这里等你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.05,1:32:36.13,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Nello, we're coming for you!{\r}\N尼洛 我们来找你了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.85,1:32:52.96,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Oh, no, Papa! Is he dead?{\r}\N哦 不 爸爸!他死了么?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.60,1:33:07.33,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}- Nello, I thought you were dead. - Aloise!{\r}\N-尼洛 我还以为你死了呢 -阿洛伊斯!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.40,1:33:09.85,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I saw my own funeral.{\r}\N我看到了我自己的葬礼
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.53,1:33:13.74,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}All of you were there.{\r}\N你们都在场
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.53,1:33:16.10,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Just like I see you now.{\r}\N就像现在一样
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.78,1:33:19.26,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Rubens was with me...{\r}\N鲁本斯和我在一起...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.81,1:33:22.64,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}my mother and Grandfather.{\r}\N还有我的妈妈和外祖父
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.54,1:33:28.14,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Forgive me, Nello, I'm sorry.Forgive me, forgive me.{\r}\N请原谅我 尼洛 我很抱歉 请原谅我 原谅我
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.41,1:33:48.32,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I have something.{\r}\N我有些东西
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.88,1:33:54.61,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}This was given to me when I was your age.{\r}\N这是在我和你一样年纪的时候别人给我的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.25,1:34:02.58,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}I knew you'd come.{\r}\N我知道您会来
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.78,1:34:05.09,电影,,0,0,0,,{\fntimes New Roman\b1\fs21\3c&H000000&}Just like in my dream.{\r}\N就像我的梦中一样
